 <text id="F3001T">
  <front id="d2">
   <div1 type="summary" id="d3">
    <p>Demus comments on the value of receiving letters and mentions his company's recent movement
     through Charleston, South Carolina.</p>
   </div1>
  </front>

  <body id="d4">
   <div1 type="letter" id="d5">
    <head>
     <name type="recipient">Mary Jane Demus</name>
    </head>

    <opener>
     <dateline>
      <date value="1865-04-04"><orig reg="April">Aprile</orig> the 4th 1865</date>
      <name type="place"><orig reg="Georgetown">gorge town</orig> south <orig reg="Carolina"
       >Carlina</orig><lb/> Camp 54th Mass <orig reg="volunteers">volintears</orig></name>
     </dateline>
     <salute><orig reg="My">Mi</orig> Dear</salute>
    </opener>

    <p>I take this present <orig reg="opportunity">opituity</orig> to <orig reg="Read">Reat</orig>
     you a <orig reg="few">fu</orig> lines to inform you that I am Well at present and i hope</p>

    <p><orig reg="When">Whean</orig> these <orig reg="few">fu</orig> lines Reach you <orig
      reg="they">tha</orig>
     <orig reg="May">Ma</orig> find you in the <orig reg="same">sam</orig> state of <orig
      reg="health">healt</orig>
     <orig reg="My">Mi</orig> Dear I <orig reg="have">heave</orig>
     <orig reg="Wrote">Rote</orig>
     <orig reg="three">thee</orig> or <orig reg="four">for</orig> letters to you But i <orig
      reg="have">heave</orig>
     <orig reg="been">bean</orig>
     <orig reg="Moving">Moveing</orig>
     <orig reg="around">a Rond</orig> so much that i Did Not <orig reg="Know">Now</orig></p>

    <p><orig reg="Whether">Wether</orig> you got it or Not and the last letter I <orig reg="Receive"
      >Receave</orig>
     <orig reg="from">frum</orig> you <orig reg="Why">Wiy</orig> it Was such a Nice letter that I
      <orig reg="Was">Wos</orig> sorry that I had <orig reg="Wrote">Rot</orig> such a letter as i
     Did But i hope that you Will <orig reg="excuse">excus</orig> Me for it for i Was very
      <unclear>andrun</unclear> at that <orig reg="time">tim</orig></p>

    <p>But <orig reg="When">Whean</orig> i got this last letter <orig reg="Why">Wiy</orig> it Was
      <unclear>somien</unclear>
     <orig reg="like">lik</orig> a letter and I hope that all the Rest Will be <orig reg="like"
     >lik</orig> it for then i am very happy to get a letter But <orig reg="When">Whean</orig>
     <orig reg="they">tha</orig>
     <orig reg="Come">Cum</orig>
     <orig reg="like">lik</orig>
     <orig reg="they">tha</orig> Did for <orig reg="awhile">a While</orig>
     <orig reg="Why">Wiy</orig> it <orig reg="goes">gos</orig>
     <orig reg="very">verry</orig> hard With Me <orig reg="for">fer</orig> i hated to open the
     letter <orig reg="for">fer</orig> after i <orig reg="Would">Wod</orig></p>

    <p>Read it <orig reg="Why">Wiy</orig> then I <orig reg="Could">Cod</orig> go <orig reg="off"
     >of</orig> to <orig reg="Myself">Mi Celf</orig> and set Down and study <orig reg="about">a
     bout</orig> it but Now if you <orig reg="Would">Wod</orig>
     <orig reg="Write">Rit</orig> every <orig reg="week">weak</orig>
     <orig reg="Why">Wiy</orig> it <orig reg="Would">Wod</orig> Not be too often <orig reg="for"
     >fer</orig> Me <orig reg="for">fer</orig> We <orig reg="have">heave</orig>
     <orig reg="been">bean</orig>
     <unclear>trubel</unclear>
     <orig reg="for">fer</orig>
     <orig reg="some">som</orig>
     <orig reg="time">tim</orig> I left the <unclear>Comasar</unclear> and <orig reg="joined"
     >jonge</orig> the <orig reg="Regiment">Redgmen</orig> in <orig reg="Charleston">Charston</orig>
     <orig reg="city">sity</orig> and then We Went to the <orig reg="city">sity</orig> of <orig
      reg="savannah">suvenayh</orig>
     <orig reg="georgia">gorges</orig> and We <orig reg="stayed">stad</orig>
     <orig reg="there">thear</orig> for <orig reg="two">too</orig>
     <orig reg="weeks">weaks</orig> and then We</p>

    <p>left and Went Back to <orig reg="Charleston">Charlston</orig>
     <orig reg="city">sity</orig> and <orig reg="stayed">stad</orig>
     <orig reg="there">theare</orig> 5 Days and then We left and <orig reg="Came">Cam</orig> to
      <orig reg="Georgetown">gorge town</orig> south <orig reg="Carolina">Carlina</orig> and i <orig
      reg="Can't">Cant</orig> tell how long We Will be <orig reg="here">hear</orig>
     <orig reg="for">fer</orig></p>

    <p><orig reg="there">thear</orig> is <del rend="none" hand="h1"/>
     <unclear>Cumey</unclear>
     <unclear>rdy</unclear> to pack up for to leave and i <orig reg="Can't">Cant</orig> tell <orig
      reg="Where">Whear</orig>
     <orig reg="they">tha</orig>
     <orig reg="are">ar</orig> going and Now <orig reg="there">thear</orig> it is time <orig
      reg="for">fer</orig> Me to get Ready for <orig reg="dress">dres</orig>
     <orig reg="parade">perrade</orig></p>

    <p>Nothing <orig reg="More">Mor</orig> at present But still <orig reg="Remain">Reman</orig></p>

    <closer>
     <salute><orig reg="your">yor</orig> Dear <orig reg="husband">husben</orig></salute>
     <signed>David A. Demus to his Dear Wife Mrs. Mary Jane Demus</signed>
     <seg type="postscript"><orig reg="please">pleas</orig>
      <orig reg="Write">Rit</orig>
      <orig reg="soon">son</orig> Direct <orig reg="your">yor</orig> letter to <orig
       reg="georgetown">gorge town</orig> south <orig reg="Carolina">Carlina</orig><lb/> Camp 54th
      Mass <orig reg="volunteers">voluntear</orig><lb/>
      <abbr expan="Company">Co</abbr>K<lb/>
      <orig reg="Samuel">samel</orig> and Jacop and <orig reg="Joseph">Jophes</orig> and <orig
       reg="My">Mi</orig>
      <orig reg="brother">bruther</orig>
      <orig reg="George">gorge</orig> send his love to you <orig reg="My">Mi</orig> Dear i just
       <orig reg="have">haft</orig> to fall in to leave on and <orig reg="suppose">suppos</orig> i
       <orig reg="can't">cant</orig> tell <orig reg="where">whear</orig> but the letter Will <orig
       reg="follow">folo</orig> the <orig reg="Regiment">Readgment</orig></seg>
    </closer>
   </div1>
  </body>
